---
// About section — bio and skills
---

<div class="mb-16">
  <h2 class="font-display text-3xl text-accent mb-8">// about</h2>
  <p class="text-text-primary leading-relaxed mb-4">
    Hi, my name is Micah Ice. I'm a high school developer who specializes in
    building apps and tools. This is a collection of my apps and projects that
    I've been building since January 2026. If you're interested in building your
    own apps or want me to make one for you, email me below.
  </p>
  <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-6">
    {['17 Years Old', 'Entrepreneur', 'High School Developer', 'App Builder', 'Self-Taught'].map((skill) => (
      <span class="text-xs font-mono text-accent-alt border border-border px-3 py-1 rounded">
        {skill}
      </span>
    ))}
  </div>
</div>
